11 An Act relating to unstable housing; creating the
Student Eviction Assistance Pilot Program Revolving
12 Fund; directing the State Department of Education to
use the fund to provide legal representation to
13 certain parties in forcible entry and detainer
actions; providing requirements to qualify for
14 representation; directing the State Board of
Education to determine service area for the legal
15 services providing the representation; providing for
administrative fee; providing requirements to qualify
16 for funding; defining term; requiring contracted
organizations to determine the eligibility of
17 individuals seeking legal services; requiring certain
report; providing for certain recordkeeping;
18 requiring an annual audit; providing for costs
related to audit; requiring audit by the State
19 Auditor and Inspector or independent auditing firm;
providing for expiration of pilot program; providing
20 for codification; and providing an effective date.
21
